      • getStockingUsers

        QiitaPageResponse<java.util.List<User>> getStockingUsers(java.lang.String itemId,
                                                         int page,
                                                         int perPage)
                                                  throws QiitaException
        Returns the users who are stocking the item in descending order of stocked time. Can be used even with unauthenticated.
        Parameters:
        itemId - the target item identifier
        page - the page number(perPage > 0 && perPage <= 100)
        perPage - the amount of users included per page(perPage > 0 && perPage <= 100)
        Returns:
        the users who is stocking the item in the page
        Throws:
        QiitaException - if arguments are incorrect or Qiita API is unavailable
